---
import SecondaryLayout from "../layouts/SecondaryLayout.astro";
---

<SecondaryLayout headerName="About Us">
  <section id="about" class="other font-running text-2xl my-8 md:my-16 p-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="font-running mt-2 text-2xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <img
            src="./images/banner.png"
            style="max-height: 300px"
            class="max-width-full rounded shadow-lg mx-auto inline"
          />
        </div>

        Welcome to the team of NewTaber, your number one source for all things
        Online / Software world. We're dedicated to providing you the very best
        of the software world, with an emphasis on simplicity, easy to use,
        free.

        <br /><br />

        Founded by a team of enthuse developers, NewTaber has come a long way
        from its beginnings. When we first started out, the passion for the
        "NewTaber" drove them to start their own business.

        <br /><br />

        We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you.
        If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact
        us.

        <br /><br />

        Sincerely, NewTaber Team.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SecondaryLayout>
